Author: livipup
Text: [I'm not sure this will help very much, but it might.](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1WkN8W15lEhz3567KQl3VIKPrBhOyupuH75i7XaON8W4/edit?usp=sharing) I do have more info I can share if you're interested in any particular plan. I wouldn't say that any of them are too great, but they're at least healthy. Like, a few of them literally requiring eating almost an entire cantaloupe. I also used a lot of supplements and kind of lean heavily on this smoothie recipe I really like. I think #11 is probably the easiest one for someone who is unprepared, but it also isn't very good because it's so low in calories.
